
### constant vs normal variable

| Feature | Constant (`const`) | Variable (`let`) |
| --- | --- | --- |
| Mutability | Always immutable | Immutable by default, can be mutable |
| Type Annotation | Required | Optional (inferred by compiler) |
| Scope | Global within the module | Block (function) scoped |
| Value | Must be known at compile-time | Can be assigned at runtime |
| Syntax | `const` keyword | `let` keyword |